Package org.docheinstein.mp3doctor.artist.impl

  • Class Summary 
    Class Description
    MusicArtistImpl
    Represents an abstract implementation of MusicArtist which let the fields to be get and set and furthermore implements the Observable interface which may help to listen to changes of this entity.
    MusicGroupImpl
    Represents a basic implementation of MusicArtistImpl for a Group, which let the fields to be get and set and furthermore implements the Observable interface which may help to listen to changes of this entity.
    SoloMusicArtistImpl
    Represents a basic implementation of MusicArtistImpl for a Person, which let the fields to be get and set and furthermore implements the Observable interface which may help to listen to changes of this entity.
